metadata.name: Jiggy #35
metadata.description: The Jiggys are a vibrant collection of 9,444 randomly generated NFTs chilling on the Ethereum Blockchain. Each Jiggy has its own energy, feelings, traits, and vibes. All Jiggys want to be heard, express themselves freely, and share a good time with everyone. Every Jiggy will dance, play, explore, and discover all the secrets to the JiggyVerse. Learn more at https://TheJiggys.com and experience the game being built at https://JiggyVerse.com
